Quote:  "We call it the 'bonk scale'... If we think someone is slowing, we ask them where they are on the scale. A 1 means, 'I am bonking' - hitting the wall - 'dig a hole and bury me.' A 10 means, 'I'm feeling great - I'll carry you up the next hill.'"
